(5765, '_transient_woosuite-all-plugins', 'a:20:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":19:{s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Sales Agents\";s:4:\"slug\";s:15:\"woo-sales-agent\";s:4:\"path\";s:35:\"woo-sales-agent/woo-sales-agent.php\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:6:\"author\";s:43:\"<a href=\"https://woosuite.com\">Woosuite</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:20:\"https://woosuite.com\";s:8:\"requires\";s:5:\"6.1.1\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"6.1.1\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.6\";s:10:\"downloaded\";i:176;s:6:\"clicks\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"last_date_updated\";s:22:\"2022-12-01 11:50am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2021-08-11\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:46:\"https://woosuite.com/plugins/sales-agent-reps/\";s:8:\"sections\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:11:\"description\";s:164:\"Sales Agent for WooCommerce is your solution for managing your company\'s sales agents and their commissions. While sales agents create new customer profiles and ...\";s:3:\"faq\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:2471:\"\n<h4>Version: 1.1.0 - [2022-12-01 11:50 AM]</h4>* Prevent redirection after creating a new customer from the sale agent dashboard\r\n* Integrate agent reference code with WC native coupon system\r\n* Reworked agent dashboard page to run separately from the WC pages\r\n* Added support for sales agent cart editing\n<h4>Version: 1.0.9 - [2022-10-26 2:18 PM]</h4>* Added reference code input field on the checkout page\r\n* Exclude the commission metadata from displaying on the frontend\n<h4>Version: 1.0.8 - [2022-10-17 12:33 PM]</h4>* Add option to restrict sale agent from placing order on behalf of customers\r\n* Add option to allow custom reference code to link customers to sales agent on signup \r\n* Allow sales agents to see the company name on their list of customers \n<h4>Version: 1.0.7 - [2022-09-12 1:13 PM]</h4>* Add support to show custom fields from our user registration plugin\r\n* Redirect sales agent to dashboard after login\r\n* Add pot file for translations \n<h4>Version: 1.0.6 - [2022-08-03 2:26 PM]</h4>* Optimize the query and bugs fixes\n<h4>Version: 1.0.5 - [2022-05-19 1:12 PM]</h4>* Added option to change the referral link\r\n* Added option to add signup commission\r\n* Added to so reps a create custom shop or product link\r\n* Added affiliates menu on sidebar\r\n* Added recent signups and recent commissions\r\n* Added support to allow sales agents to manage different roles\n<h4>Version: 1.0.4 - [2022-02-06 1:58 PM]</h4>* Added option to export commission\r\n* Added sales agent filter on the order page\r\n* Added export order option\n<h4>Version: 1.0.3 - [2021-12-25 1:16 AM]</h4>* Added setting fields for the commission on the settings page\r\n* Saved data to order when creating a new order\r\n* Add fields setting commission in the User edit page\r\n* Add fields to set the commission value for each product\r\n* Added a Commission page in admin to list all the orders that have Commission and allow to set it as paid/unpaid\r\n* Updated the meta box when editing the Order with more information and allow to edit the Sale agent user, created by type as well as the Order item to be applied the commission\r\n* Add 2 columns to the Orders list to show the Sales agent user as well as the Commission amount\r\n* Dashboard page for the Sale agent users\n<h4>Version: 1.0.2 - [2021-09-01 9:18 PM]</h4>* updated setting form field design and the save message.\n<h4>Version: 1.0.1 - [2021-08-29 1:48 PM]</h4>* add manage link when active\n<h4>Version: 1.0.0 - [2021-08-11 6:53 PM]</h4>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:164:\"Sales Agent for WooCommerce is your solution for managing your company\'s sales agents and their commissions. While sales agents create new customer profiles and ...\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:65:\"https://dw.woosuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/sale-agent.png\";s:2:\"2x\";s:65:\"https://dw.woosuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/sale-agent.png\";}s:19:\"recommended_plugins\";s:616:\"s:607:\"a:4:{i:1;a:5:{s:6:\"plugin\";s:3