upon code trigger for fees and bundle discount\r\n* Add \"You save\" feature\r\n* Add bundle pricing\n<h4>Version: 1.3.2 - [2022-04-14 2:42 PM]</h4>* Add option to apply rules based on selected users\r\n* Removing unused variables\r\n* Add checkout fee\r\n* Add discount price column\r\n* Fix variation pricing discount\r\n* Fix warning issues on PHP8\r\n* Add first-time buyer condition\r\n* Replacing the regex with the compatible version with Safari browser\n<h4>Version: 1.3.1 - [2022-03-07 5:17 PM]</h4>* Added support for the product with price at 0\r\n* Added support for the pricing rule with Amount as the float\r\n* Fixed the live price JS change\r\n* Add support to work with both dot and comma decimal separator\r\n* Fix variation products get discounted twice\r\n* Excluding the variation price from re-calculating discount\r\n* Added support export tiered pricing\r\n* Added support to import tiered pricing rules\r\n* Check active buffer before flushing\r\n* Convert boolean to int to fix PHP8 compatible\n<h4>Version: 1.3.0 - [2022-03-01 10:23 PM]</h4>* Added additional column to show the discounted price\r\n* Added check product instance of WC_Product before using its methods\r\n* Fixed cart discount issue\n<h4>Version: 1.2.9 - [2022-02-11 11:15 AM]</h4>* Added full tiered pricing support\r\n* Fixed PHP8 compatibility issues\n<h4>Version: 1.2.8 - [2022-02-06 3:43 PM]</h4>* Update to enqueue JS when needed only\r\n* Optimize the product query\r\n* Added WooCommerce Subscription support\r\n* Added Advanced Rules Tab\r\n* Fix the variable product price\r\n* Fix order qty on the cart page\r\n* Added pricing table display control\n<h4>Version: 1.2.7 - [2021-08-29 1:37 PM]</h4>* Fixed confliction with Woosuite wholesale pricing\n<h4>Version: 1.2.6 - [2021-08-11 6:29 PM]</h4>* Woosuite rebrand and added bulk import/export feature\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:109:\"Whether that is on a user role basis, minimum order amount, per product category or even within a date ran